f(n)=\frac{n+1}{r+1}
n\ge r
 \begin{align}f(n)&=\frac{{n-1\choose r-1}+\left({n\choose r}-{n-1\choose r-1}\right)(1+f(n-1)}{n\choose r}\\&=1+\left(1-\frac{n-1\choose r-1}{n\choose r}\right)f(n-1)\\&=1+\left(1-\frac{r}{n}\right)f(n-1).\end{align}
