\{1, 2, \ldots, n\}
\mu_{n,r-1} = \frac{n+1}{r-1 +1} = \frac{n+1}{r}
\mu_{n+1,r}
\binom{n}{r-1} \frac{n+1}{r} = \binom{n+1}{r}
\binom{n}{r} \frac{n+1}{r+1} = \binom{n+1}{r+1}
 \mu_{n+1,r} = \frac{\binom{n}{r-1} \frac{n+1}{r} + \binom{n}{r} \frac{n+1}{r+1}}{\binom{n+1}{r}} \, . 
 \mu_{n+1,r} = \frac{\binom{n+1}{r} + \binom{n+1}{r+1}}{\binom{n+1}{r}} = \frac{\binom{n+2}{r+1}}{\binom{n+1}{r}} = \frac{n+2}{r+1} 
